==Description==
The '''Max Revive''' is a type of [[Underground|Underground Item]].

==Details==
The '''Max Revive''' has a value of 4 [[Diamonds]] {{Diamonds}} when sold. It can also be traded in Daily Deals. 

==Mine Layout==
The Max Revive appears in the Underground as a 3x3 sized object.<br><br>
